# Cortex v3.0 Demo - Claude's Cognitive Layer
# Records terminal output as an animated GIF

Output assets/demo.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 20

Type "node scripts/demo-neural-visuals.cjs nodes"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "node bin/cortex.cjs status"
Enter
Sleep 3s
